WEBVTT

01:27.400 --> 01:31.840
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.120 --> 01:34.950
[Episode 6]

01:35.039 --> 01:38.420
[Lihai University]

01:38.490 --> 01:42.509
[PARKING FULL]

01:42.570 --> 01:45.220
[CERTIFICATE OF HONORARY APPOINTMENT]

01:43.870 --> 01:45.080
Wow, it's been ages.

01:46.590 --> 01:47.509
You were always

01:47.509 --> 01:49.509
hard to find back in our school days.

01:49.789 --> 01:52.990
It's practically been a decade
since graduation, right?

01:53.030 --> 01:55.200
You never show up to
our alumni gatherings.

01:55.200 --> 01:57.509
Still, we've all seen your papers
published nonstop.

01:57.509 --> 01:59.110
You're way ahead of the rest.

02:00.040 --> 02:01.300
You're flattering me.

02:01.560 --> 02:02.790
You've published plenty of papers too.

02:02.790 --> 02:03.850
I've read them all.

02:06.640 --> 02:07.000
Here,

02:07.350 --> 02:08.000
try this.

02:09.030 --> 02:10.669
I heard about your

02:10.960 --> 02:12.150
professional title review.

02:12.150 --> 02:14.190
Will it affect your reappointment?

02:14.590 --> 02:16.150
I can put in a good word for you,
pull some strings behind the scenes.

02:16.150 --> 02:16.840
Though honestly...

02:16.840 --> 02:18.770
as the head of a secondary college,

02:19.030 --> 02:20.690
my influence only goes so far.

02:21.470 --> 02:22.350
Thanks.

02:23.190 --> 02:24.520
But I'm actually here

02:24.750 --> 02:26.910
to ask your wife a favor.

02:28.280 --> 02:28.940
Zhou Mi?

02:35.280 --> 02:36.740
Sorry to keep you waiting.

02:36.960 --> 02:38.420
It's fine, I just got here.

02:38.680 --> 02:39.540
Come on, get in.

02:42.150 --> 02:44.130
Why did you insist on picking me up today?

02:44.130 --> 02:45.220
Just missed you.

02:46.590 --> 02:46.920
Fine.

02:48.190 --> 02:49.850
But that doesn't convince me.

03:00.470 --> 03:01.560
Alright, fine. I do need

03:01.560 --> 03:02.890
a tiny favor, actually.

03:04.680 --> 03:06.740
You remember my old friend, Yan Ling?

03:08.000 --> 03:08.860
I remember her.

03:09.590 --> 03:10.190
The famous

03:10.400 --> 03:14.060
campus beauty that got caught  in
the drama with someone's family?

03:15.710 --> 03:16.910
She's come to you now?

03:17.360 --> 03:18.030
It's not me

03:18.030 --> 03:18.520
she's looking for.

03:18.520 --> 03:19.470
It's you.

03:20.030 --> 03:22.290
Apparently she needs your help on a case.

03:22.630 --> 03:23.360
Not doing it.

03:23.430 --> 03:24.360
You're saying no before you even know

03:24.360 --> 03:25.300
what the case is?

03:25.750 --> 03:26.750
I don't know her at all.

03:26.750 --> 03:27.520
I've never liked her.

03:27.520 --> 03:28.800
And I want nothing to do with her.

03:28.800 --> 03:29.200
Drive.

03:30.750 --> 03:32.840
Come on, you're always so quick to judge.

03:32.840 --> 03:35.630
Not everyone is as upright and
principled as you are.

03:35.630 --> 03:36.430
Right, honey?

03:37.430 --> 03:38.240
I'll grab a cab instead.

03:38.240 --> 03:38.810
Fine. Let's go.

03:38.810 --> 03:39.360
Let's go.

03:40.870 --> 03:42.600
I'll take you for hot pot later.

03:43.630 --> 03:44.460
I heard

03:44.520 --> 03:45.520
her husband

03:45.520 --> 03:47.240
is a high-profile businessman.

03:47.240 --> 03:48.620
Taking this case

03:48.870 --> 03:50.590
will definitely work in your favor.

03:50.590 --> 03:51.160
Drive.

03:51.400 --> 03:51.930
Alright.

03:53.340 --> 03:56.090
[Xinsheng International Law Firm]

03:59.710 --> 04:00.770
You must be Ms. Yan.

04:01.400 --> 04:02.560
Attorney Zhou is waiting for you inside.

04:02.560 --> 04:03.490
Okay, thank you.

04:12.680 --> 04:14.480
Any fresh injuries on your body?

04:30.190 --> 04:33.320
Do you have the police evidence
records from the report?

04:33.390 --> 04:34.090
Not this time.

04:34.090 --> 04:35.690
What about medical records?

04:36.570 --> 04:37.570
I had them before.

04:37.600 --> 04:39.200
Which hospital treated you?

04:39.480 --> 04:41.390
All these pieces of evidence are critical.

04:41.390 --> 04:42.430
They can help you

04:42.430 --> 04:43.750
gain more favorable terms
in the divorce case.

04:43.750 --> 04:45.870
We might even press charges against
your husband for his illegal acts.

04:45.870 --> 04:47.130
I don't want to do that.

04:48.070 --> 04:48.909
Ms. Zhou.

04:49.590 --> 04:50.280
Ling.

04:51.720 --> 04:54.159
I... I don't want to make things
hard for Liu Ping.

04:54.159 --> 04:56.240
I never thought it would come to this.

04:56.950 --> 04:59.070
But I just can't let him hit me again.

05:03.240 --> 05:04.800
The last time he hurt me,

05:05.500 --> 05:07.470
he even wrote me a pledge.

05:13.920 --> 05:15.840
This written pledge is great
for your case.

05:15.840 --> 05:17.770
All key points are clearly stated.

05:17.800 --> 05:18.630
It can indeed be regarded as

05:18.630 --> 05:20.890
a marital property division agreement.

05:24.310 --> 05:24.920
Come in.

05:25.360 --> 05:27.650
Attorney Zhou, here are the client
power of attorney documents,

05:27.650 --> 05:29.250
and the camera you asked for.

05:32.159 --> 05:34.630
This is the retainer agreement for
Attorney Zhou's legal representation.

05:34.630 --> 05:35.390
Please take a look.

05:35.390 --> 05:36.560
Sign it if you agree.

05:38.560 --> 05:39.560
Thank you so much.

05:40.000 --> 05:42.240
-As for the legal fees...
-Pay me after

05:42.310 --> 05:44.240
you get your property settlement.

05:49.920 --> 05:51.120
If you agree,

05:51.560 --> 05:52.760
I'll take some photos

05:53.120 --> 05:54.450
to secure the evidence.

06:35.480 --> 06:36.680
After technical screening,

06:36.680 --> 06:37.950
No matching information found
for Pongsri Leekpa

06:37.950 --> 06:39.500
in our country's ID and

06:39.600 --> 06:41.560
household registration system.

06:43.510 --> 06:44.909
Let's go, time for lunch.

06:46.190 --> 06:46.870
Time for lunch.

06:46.870 --> 06:47.740
Okay, coming.

06:48.800 --> 06:50.360
Let's go, Pangpang. Let's go
get spicy crab.

06:50.360 --> 06:51.159
I'm not going.

06:51.190 --> 06:52.920
You don't even want spicy crab?

06:53.070 --> 06:55.530
I feel sick just hearing
the word 'crab' now.

06:56.240 --> 06:57.630
Oh? You're actually trying to
lose weight, Pangpang?

06:57.630 --> 06:59.360
Got a crush on someone, don't you?

06:59.360 --> 07:00.190
Cut it out.

07:00.190 --> 07:00.870
Him in a relationship?

07:00.870 --> 07:01.800
With who even?

07:03.160 --> 07:04.280
With crabs.

07:04.310 --> 07:05.070
Alright.

07:05.360 --> 07:06.070
You're really not eating?

07:06.070 --> 07:07.240
Alright then, I'm heading out.

07:07.240 --> 07:07.750
Go ahead.

07:07.750 --> 07:13.470
[China Police]

07:18.440 --> 07:18.980
Mom.

07:22.630 --> 07:24.120
Stop fussig about it.

07:24.120 --> 07:25.830
I don't have time for this.

07:31.560 --> 07:33.180
You've got a fuller face,

07:33.310 --> 07:35.680
but your bone structure's actually great.

07:35.680 --> 07:37.040
No need for jaw contouring surgery.

07:37.040 --> 07:40.500
Just get some face slimming shots
or liposuction, that’ll do.

07:40.800 --> 07:42.430
And an eye corner enlargement surgery.

07:42.430 --> 07:43.390
Bigger eyes

07:43.390 --> 07:44.950
will naturally make your face
look smaller.

07:44.950 --> 07:46.420
Add my work WeChat first,

07:46.560 --> 07:48.020
we can chat on there later.

07:50.870 --> 07:51.659
Sorry.

07:51.720 --> 07:52.159
I mean

07:53.870 --> 07:55.720
I really don't have

07:56.870 --> 07:58.360
any plans to get plastic surgery
right now.

07:58.360 --> 08:01.220
Then do you even plan on dating
and getting married?

08:02.750 --> 08:03.720
If you did,

08:03.870 --> 08:04.600
you wouldn't

08:04.600 --> 08:06.270
pig out right off the bat.

08:07.070 --> 08:09.160
We're both just here
to please our parents

08:09.160 --> 08:10.420
and get this over with,

08:10.430 --> 08:12.390
and I don't wanna waste my time either.

08:12.390 --> 08:13.360
Just add my contact first.

08:13.360 --> 08:14.800
It's like this blind date.

08:14.800 --> 08:15.600
You didn’t wanna come,

08:15.600 --> 08:16.800
but you showed up anyway.

08:16.800 --> 08:18.680
What if later you meet a girl you like,

08:18.680 --> 08:19.510
and then you wanna get work done?

08:19.510 --> 08:20.570
You've got a point.

08:23.040 --> 08:26.390
Guys getting plastic surgery are
quite common these days, huh?

08:26.390 --> 08:27.190
You're right.

08:27.390 --> 08:29.120
Everyone loves beauty, after all.

08:29.120 --> 08:31.070
Loads of guys come to me for procedures,
and when they go home,

08:31.070 --> 08:34.530
they’re so handsome even their
own moms can’t recognize them.

08:36.900 --> 08:38.490
Can you take a look for me?

08:39.360 --> 08:40.090
This person,

08:40.840 --> 08:42.370
has he had plastic surgery?

08:42.669 --> 08:44.940
[Reduce earlobes, fill nasolabial folds
and nasal base.]

08:44.000 --> 08:45.720
This is just for fun,

08:44.960 --> 08:47.330
[Reshape the mandibular angle.]

08:45.840 --> 08:47.370
nothing official about it.

08:47.790 --> 08:50.120
Even a casual sketch still looks spot-on.

08:50.790 --> 08:52.750
You've never even seen what he looked
like before plastic surgery,

08:52.750 --> 08:54.880
so how would you know if it’s accurate?

08:55.120 --> 08:55.840
When Ms. Sun draws,

08:55.840 --> 08:57.170
she never gets it wrong.

08:57.440 --> 08:58.840
I only drew this based on

08:58.840 --> 09:00.670
the cosmetic surgery records you provided,

09:00.670 --> 09:03.530
relying entirely on imagination
and speculation.

09:04.150 --> 09:04.960
Even if he’s had so much plastic surgery

09:04.960 --> 09:06.150
his own mom wouldn’t recognize him,

09:06.150 --> 09:08.210
Ms. Sun can still draw him perfectly.

09:08.240 --> 09:09.840
Alright, quit your teasing.

09:16.480 --> 09:19.010
You little rascal, think you can
hide from us?

09:20.760 --> 09:21.440
And then?

09:23.320 --> 09:24.670
Where are you going to find him

09:24.670 --> 09:25.800
with this portrait?

09:33.270 --> 09:38.670
[Technical Department]

09:39.960 --> 09:40.790
Hey. Hey.

09:42.870 --> 09:44.000
Looking for Ms. Sun?

09:47.120 --> 09:48.670
Chihuahua succulents don't work anymore.

09:48.670 --> 09:51.130
Too many. I've already
given her three pots.

09:51.200 --> 09:52.880
Next time, get some

09:53.240 --> 09:54.550
Black rabbit ear succulent.

09:54.550 --> 09:55.610
That works better.

09:57.200 --> 09:57.800
Thank you.

09:57.870 --> 09:58.800
You're welcome.

10:02.510 --> 10:03.120
Hello.

10:03.790 --> 10:04.390
Hi.

10:04.390 --> 10:05.320
Long time no see.

10:05.320 --> 10:05.670
Look.

10:05.670 --> 10:06.440
I missed you.

10:07.790 --> 10:09.150
How did you know I like this kind?

10:09.150 --> 10:10.240
Of course I do.

10:10.240 --> 10:10.720
Come.

10:10.720 --> 10:12.650
Take a look at my succulent garden.

10:15.030 --> 10:15.830
Today.

10:15.910 --> 10:16.440
I've got

10:16.720 --> 10:17.650
two more pots.

10:18.510 --> 10:21.240
[Blind Therapist Massage]

10:43.520 --> 10:43.960
[New friends]

10:43.960 --> 10:44.680
[A Leaf of Loneliness]

10:44.810 --> 10:45.470
[Xu Feng] [How are you?
I miss you so much.]

10:45.490 --> 10:47.540
[Xu Feng] [Please don't shut me out.]

10:47.600 --> 10:48.550
How are you?

10:49.240 --> 10:50.240
I miss you so much.

10:51.550 --> 10:53.150
Please don't shut me out.

10:54.910 --> 10:55.480
Changning.

10:55.190 --> 10:55.800
[Accept Friend Request]

10:55.830 --> 10:56.060
[Processing]

10:56.000 --> 10:56.870
I'll never meet another girl

10:56.870 --> 10:58.200
as gentle, pure

10:58.200 --> 10:59.870
and considerate as you.

10:58.890 --> 11:01.140
[A Leaf of Loneliness]

11:00.630 --> 11:02.030
I can't live without you.

11:04.600 --> 11:06.800
I miss the soup you used to cook so badly.

11:06.870 --> 11:09.000
The world feels so lonely without you.

11:09.440 --> 11:10.100
Changning,

11:10.600 --> 11:12.360
please don't leave me, okay?

11:13.950 --> 11:17.150
[I can't live without you.]

11:18.550 --> 11:19.240
Changning.

11:19.940 --> 11:21.800
Do you still remember this place?

11:22.120 --> 11:23.500
Now I realize that day

11:23.630 --> 11:26.960
was the happiest moment of my life.

11:29.450 --> 11:30.360
Darling,

11:30.520 --> 11:32.450
I want to see you in those

11:32.600 --> 11:35.440
black lace garters tonight.

11:35.050 --> 11:35.450
[Stop it!]

11:35.470 --> 11:35.880
[See you soon, babe. I'm
looking forward to it!]

11:35.510 --> 11:36.080
Love you.

11:36.390 --> 11:37.320
Babe, I'm here.

11:37.440 --> 11:38.320
Waiting for you.

11:38.320 --> 11:40.320
Did you wear the clothes I told you to?

11:40.320 --> 11:41.790
I'll tell you when you get here.

11:41.790 --> 11:42.960
Then when we meet later,

11:42.960 --> 11:44.960
I'm gonna give you a thorough check.

11:45.240 --> 11:46.440
You are such a tease!

11:46.480 --> 11:47.910
And only to you.

11:54.390 --> 11:55.190
What the heck?

11:55.490 --> 11:56.860
You bitch!

12:02.000 --> 12:03.240
Stay away from Feng,

12:03.320 --> 12:05.780
or I'll throw sulfuric acid
at you next time!

12:35.200 --> 12:35.840
Feng.

12:36.320 --> 12:38.320
It's her right to like me.

12:38.480 --> 12:40.680
How dare you even splash her with paint?

12:40.960 --> 12:41.910
If you can suspect me of
cheating like this,

12:41.910 --> 12:43.050
would you kill me next time?

12:43.050 --> 12:44.240
How could I?

12:44.890 --> 12:46.650
I know you'd never cheat on me.

12:46.680 --> 12:47.790
It's all those cheap women's fault!

12:47.790 --> 12:49.320
You're way too possessive.

12:49.510 --> 12:51.600
You spend every day here, drinking
with men, smiling to please them,

12:51.600 --> 12:52.840
being groped while dressed like this.

12:52.840 --> 12:54.170
And did I ever say a word?

12:54.550 --> 12:55.120
Yuan Ye.

12:55.520 --> 12:57.250
I think we should call it quits.

12:57.670 --> 12:59.530
Let's stop torturing each other.

12:59.750 --> 13:01.120
I know I was wrong!

13:01.120 --> 13:02.630
I'll definitely change next time, I swear!

13:02.630 --> 13:04.600
I'm so sorry.

13:04.600 --> 13:06.270
I'm so sorry. I'm sorry.

13:07.080 --> 13:09.910
I promise I'll never do this again.

13:09.910 --> 13:11.840
I promise, never ever!

13:11.870 --> 13:12.720
I know. I get it.

13:12.720 --> 13:14.190
Hit me! Go on, hit me!

13:14.240 --> 13:15.750
You'll feel better once you do it.

13:15.750 --> 13:16.670
Hit me.

13:16.670 --> 13:18.470
-I don’t hit women.
-I’m fine...

13:19.560 --> 13:21.620
I could never bring myself to hit you.

13:24.600 --> 13:25.600
But if you don't suffer a little,

13:25.600 --> 13:27.400
you'll never learn your lesson.

13:29.360 --> 13:30.380
Then tell me.

13:30.870 --> 13:31.870
Tell me what to do!

13:33.670 --> 13:35.600
I'll do anything, anything at all,

13:35.640 --> 13:37.250
as long as you don't leave me!

13:50.960 --> 13:51.880
Really?

13:54.750 --> 13:55.780
Anything?

14:02.640 --> 14:04.410
Then carve a maple leaf here.

14:06.350 --> 14:07.550
Carve it with a knife.

14:11.120 --> 14:12.060
Can you do that?

14:14.170 --> 14:14.910
Yes.

15:09.790 --> 15:10.590
What's wrong?

15:12.360 --> 15:13.050
Nothing.

15:13.750 --> 15:15.920
I just accidentally bumped into something.

15:15.920 --> 15:16.520
It's fine.

15:17.910 --> 15:19.110
Let's eat breakfast.

15:19.200 --> 15:19.670
Okay.

15:35.510 --> 15:37.110
Let's not put up a tombstone.

15:37.870 --> 15:38.620
Up to you.

16:34.790 --> 16:35.650
Sister.

16:36.000 --> 16:36.390
Sister.

16:36.390 --> 16:37.440
I'm never coming back

16:37.440 --> 16:39.070
to this house again.

16:43.030 --> 16:43.630
Sister.

16:45.600 --> 16:46.360
Sister.

16:47.720 --> 16:48.390
Sister.

17:54.440 --> 17:56.040
Take it easy. We're not late.

17:56.310 --> 17:57.030
Take your time.

17:57.030 --> 17:57.440
No rush, okay?

17:57.440 --> 17:57.900
I'm off.

18:03.640 --> 18:03.920
Hello?

18:03.920 --> 18:05.350
Hello, is this Ms. Yan?

18:05.590 --> 18:07.000
Have you seen Changning?

18:07.590 --> 18:08.350
Nope.

18:08.920 --> 18:10.880
Isn't she supposed to be resting at home?

18:10.880 --> 18:12.110
The other day

18:12.480 --> 18:13.270
Changning said

18:13.270 --> 18:15.000
she wanted to go to grandma's
to see her little brother,

18:15.000 --> 18:16.510
so I let her go.

18:16.680 --> 18:18.640
Just now, my family called.

18:19.200 --> 18:20.130
Her grandma said

18:20.640 --> 18:21.750
she only stayed for a day

18:21.750 --> 18:23.150
and headed home ages ago.

18:23.400 --> 18:25.400
But she hasn't actually come back!

18:25.790 --> 18:27.270
Don't panic first.

18:28.350 --> 18:29.510
She took her phone

18:29.680 --> 18:30.980
and left with a plan.

18:31.110 --> 18:32.550
She must be in a clear state of mind.

18:32.550 --> 18:33.960
She knows exactly what she's doing.

18:33.960 --> 18:36.690
Let me ask some of her
other classmates too, okay?

18:36.880 --> 18:37.640
Okay, okay.

18:37.750 --> 18:38.720
Got it, Ms. Yan.

18:38.830 --> 18:39.830
Thank you so much!

18:40.200 --> 18:41.030
Hello, class.

18:41.030 --> 18:41.970
It's Ms. Yan.

18:42.110 --> 18:44.680
If anyone has any news about Li Changning,

18:45.000 --> 18:47.200
please let me know. Thank you!

19:14.960 --> 19:15.920
Why are you here?

19:17.160 --> 19:17.960
Where is Feng?

19:19.110 --> 19:20.240
-What are you doing?
-Feng!

19:20.240 --> 19:21.200
Get out!

19:21.200 --> 19:22.160
He is not here!

19:22.640 --> 19:23.310
-Feng!
-Stop looking!

19:23.310 --> 19:25.240
Don't you know he has a match today?

19:25.310 --> 19:26.020
Come out!

19:26.790 --> 19:28.270
Feng, stop hiding!

19:28.400 --> 19:30.000
He is not here. Stop looking.

19:30.480 --> 19:31.810
What are you doing here?

19:32.240 --> 19:34.130
Shouldn't you be back home
recovering from your illness?

19:34.130 --> 19:36.060
I should be the one asking you that!

19:37.400 --> 19:38.160
Feng said

19:38.160 --> 19:39.690
he can't stand your temper.

19:39.960 --> 19:41.400
He regrets being with you.

19:41.400 --> 19:42.570
He asked me to come back to be with him

19:42.570 --> 19:43.500
and forgive him.

19:43.640 --> 19:44.240
Bullshit!

19:44.910 --> 19:46.640
You are the one pestering Feng.

20:05.310 --> 20:06.330
[I really wish you were still by my side.]

20:06.350 --> 20:07.500
[Come back, please? Right now,
I just want to hold you tight]

20:07.520 --> 20:08.810
[and kiss you. Just the two of us.]

20:08.830 --> 20:11.270
[I find myself reliving all the beautiful
moments we shared every single second.]

20:12.590 --> 20:12.920
Hey!

20:39.160 --> 20:40.070
What is it now?

20:40.200 --> 20:41.460
Where is Li Changning?

20:42.590 --> 20:43.510
I don't know.

20:43.570 --> 20:44.280
Didn't she

20:44.440 --> 20:46.350
take a leave of absence
to recover at home?

20:46.350 --> 20:47.670
When was the last time

20:47.720 --> 20:48.640
you saw her?

20:51.320 --> 20:53.560
When we broke up.

20:53.590 --> 20:55.060
You're lying.

20:56.000 --> 20:56.730
Where is she?

20:59.200 --> 21:00.200
Suit yourself.

21:02.550 --> 21:03.340
Xu Feng!

21:06.600 --> 21:07.530
Why are you here?

21:11.220 --> 21:12.460
Why did you lie to me?

21:12.780 --> 21:14.730
Why did you go looking for
Li Changning again?

21:14.730 --> 21:16.020
Why?

21:16.040 --> 21:17.440
It was nothing but a show!

21:17.880 --> 21:19.130
She is crazy.

21:27.720 --> 21:28.250
Feng.

21:28.280 --> 21:29.310
Call an ambulance!

21:29.310 --> 21:30.390
Call an ambulance!

21:33.510 --> 21:34.340
Feng.

21:34.550 --> 21:35.420
Feng.

21:35.640 --> 21:37.190
I didn't mean it!

21:37.360 --> 21:39.140
I didn't mean it!

21:39.270 --> 21:40.350
It's all my fault!

21:40.400 --> 21:41.400
It's all my fault!

21:48.830 --> 21:49.750
Feng.

21:51.000 --> 21:51.920
Feng.

21:53.830 --> 21:54.750
Feng.

21:55.640 --> 21:56.670
Feng.

21:57.310 --> 21:58.400
Feng.

22:26.120 --> 22:27.980
Ling said she is not available today.

22:27.980 --> 22:28.760
I know.

22:29.030 --> 22:31.230
We need to verify some details with you.

22:32.280 --> 22:34.370
Sorry about the mess.

22:34.640 --> 22:35.550
Feel free to take a seat.

22:35.550 --> 22:36.300
Have a seat.

22:36.750 --> 22:37.260
You too.

22:37.480 --> 22:38.030
And you.

22:39.920 --> 22:40.940
Have some water.

22:42.070 --> 22:43.510
Here, drink up!

22:44.350 --> 22:47.350
You're pregnant. You'd better cut
down on icy drinks.

22:49.550 --> 22:50.950
Ling said the same thing.

22:51.560 --> 22:53.760
I got used to it when I was living abroad.

22:54.230 --> 22:55.160
I have to change.

22:55.830 --> 22:57.960
We have the property and partial
bank deposit documents

22:57.960 --> 22:59.720
under Liu Ping's name,

23:00.270 --> 23:01.440
plus the police inquiry records

23:01.440 --> 23:02.700
from your last report.

23:03.240 --> 23:04.640
For a better advantage

23:04.640 --> 23:06.400
in divorce and property division,

23:06.400 --> 23:07.640
we now need your

23:07.640 --> 23:09.880
pregnancy filing and medical records.

23:12.550 --> 23:15.080
Actually, I don't want
any kind of upper hand.

23:15.720 --> 23:18.590
I don't want to drag this out into
an ugly fight with Liu Ping,

23:18.590 --> 23:19.250
and I refuse

23:20.590 --> 23:23.320
to use our child as a bargaining
chip against him.

23:23.790 --> 23:24.400
So

23:25.110 --> 23:28.000
let's just stick to what's
written in the written pledge.

23:28.000 --> 23:29.240
If we go strictly by the written pledge,

23:29.240 --> 23:31.590
he'll basically end up
with nothing anyway.

23:31.590 --> 23:33.200
But we still need solid evidence

23:33.200 --> 23:34.930
to back up what's stated in it.

23:35.270 --> 23:36.550
This evidence will

23:36.590 --> 23:38.920
better protect your rights and interests

23:39.070 --> 23:41.480
So the real situation is
very important to us.

23:41.480 --> 23:42.270
He hit me.

23:42.270 --> 23:44.330
That's the absolute truth, isn't it?

23:56.210 --> 23:57.210
I know

23:57.640 --> 24:00.700
once a lawyer signs a retainer
agreement with a client,

24:01.140 --> 24:03.590
the lawyer is obligated to keep
everything confidential.

24:03.590 --> 24:06.050
Based on the principle of
zealous advocacy,

24:06.560 --> 24:08.310
if the client insists on sticking

24:08.310 --> 24:10.070
to their statement during
court cross-examination,

24:10.070 --> 24:11.070
the client can present

24:11.070 --> 24:13.640
part of the information
to the court on their own.

24:13.640 --> 24:14.790
The lawyer can stay out of it

24:14.790 --> 24:16.270
and claim no knowledge of it.

24:16.270 --> 24:17.000
Besides,

24:18.030 --> 24:19.490
isn't that why I hired you?

24:19.640 --> 24:20.750
I want to avoid

24:20.830 --> 24:22.950
going to court entirely,

24:23.070 --> 24:25.200
and just propose a divorce settlement

24:25.880 --> 24:27.480
based on his written pledge.

24:32.000 --> 24:33.800
Don't you agree, Attorney Zhou?

24:40.170 --> 24:42.430
[Emergency]

24:49.450 --> 24:50.150
Ms. Yan.

24:51.240 --> 24:52.030
Are you okay?

24:52.480 --> 24:53.480
I'm... I'm fine.

24:53.580 --> 24:54.750
How did it get this serious?

24:54.750 --> 24:56.150
It's all Xu Feng's blood.

24:56.310 --> 24:57.770
He's in surgery right now.

24:57.830 --> 24:58.400
Really?

24:59.200 --> 25:00.030
You're not hurt at all?

25:00.030 --> 25:00.960
Why are you here?

25:01.290 --> 25:03.100
Li Changning's also called me,

25:03.120 --> 25:04.950
so I took the earliest ride back.

25:05.680 --> 25:07.350
Thank you for coming all this way.

25:07.350 --> 25:09.680
There are still bloodstains on your neck.

25:12.580 --> 25:14.110
Let me wipe them off for you.

25:16.040 --> 25:16.560
May I?

25:18.100 --> 25:19.630
Okay, thanks.

25:25.480 --> 25:25.920
It's fine.

25:25.920 --> 25:27.780
I'll wash them off when I get back.

25:28.640 --> 25:29.970
Xu Feng's family?

25:30.110 --> 25:30.640
Yes, we are.

25:30.640 --> 25:30.920
Here.

25:30.920 --> 25:32.030
Xu Feng's family, right?

25:32.030 --> 25:32.590
Come here.

25:32.590 --> 25:33.200
Let me tell you,

25:33.200 --> 25:34.510
the surgery went smoothly.

25:34.510 --> 25:35.070
Fortunately,

25:35.070 --> 25:36.000
the stab wound was off-target

25:36.000 --> 25:37.510
and didn't damage any major organs.

25:37.510 --> 25:38.400
Still, he'll need

25:38.400 --> 25:39.720
quite a while to recover.

25:39.720 --> 25:40.160
Okay.

25:40.160 --> 25:41.680
Take this and go complete
the admission procedures.

25:41.680 --> 25:42.640
Okay, thank you.

25:44.360 --> 25:45.590
I've seen you both.

25:46.240 --> 25:48.150
You brought Xu Feng here.

25:48.440 --> 25:48.850
Yes.

25:48.880 --> 25:50.300
Thank you, thanks to you.

25:50.600 --> 25:52.030
For vicious assaults like this,

25:52.030 --> 25:53.920
that lunatic must go to jail.

25:54.040 --> 25:55.270
How was she even allowed on campus?

25:55.270 --> 25:56.680
Let's go check on our boy first.

25:56.680 --> 25:57.160
Okay.

25:58.680 --> 25:59.210
Let's go.

26:03.030 --> 26:05.030
It seems Xu Feng has quite a few fans.

26:11.240 --> 26:12.300
Is that your phone?

26:12.590 --> 26:13.300
Not mine.

26:18.480 --> 26:19.680
This is Xu Feng's bag.

26:19.880 --> 26:23.070
[Isolation Patient Passage]

26:23.580 --> 26:25.980
[Isolation Patient Passage]

26:35.080 --> 26:39.850
[Incoming call from Changning]

26:42.880 --> 26:43.550
Who is it?

26:43.790 --> 26:44.610
Delivery.

26:44.830 --> 26:45.630
Wait a minute.

26:51.550 --> 26:52.390
Still hiding?

26:52.610 --> 26:54.880
Do you have any idea how
worried sick your mom is?

26:54.880 --> 26:56.410
You even blocked her calls.

26:58.200 --> 26:59.830
Who told you this address?

27:00.070 --> 27:00.870
Where is Feng?

27:01.030 --> 27:02.460
Call your mom first,

27:02.640 --> 27:03.770
then we'll tell you.

27:04.340 --> 27:06.590
There must be something
wrong with Xu Feng.

27:06.590 --> 27:07.970
You think he's off too?

27:09.110 --> 27:10.480
Even if he's dating

27:10.480 --> 27:11.610
three girls at once,

27:11.960 --> 27:13.070
that'd only make him a lying playboy

27:13.070 --> 27:14.200
who gets bored easy.

27:14.720 --> 27:15.750
But look at these three girls,

27:15.750 --> 27:17.350
one's lost her mind over him,

27:17.480 --> 27:18.920
another might end up in jail for him,

27:18.920 --> 27:21.030
and the last one almost
got her face ruined.

27:21.030 --> 27:21.890
Is this normal?

27:23.400 --> 27:25.200
Even Li Changning's fallen for it too.

27:25.200 --> 27:26.750
I have no idea what spell she's under.

27:26.750 --> 27:27.880
She came back again.

27:29.750 --> 27:30.730
There are people

27:31.070 --> 27:32.680
who are experts at manipulating

27:32.680 --> 27:34.680
their partner's emotions
in a relationship.

27:34.680 --> 27:37.070
When their significant other
is obedient and loyal,

27:37.070 --> 27:38.880
they shower them with
praise and affection,

27:38.880 --> 27:40.480
making them feel utterly happy.

27:40.480 --> 27:41.540
If not, they punish them

27:41.540 --> 27:42.800
leaving them in agony.

27:43.110 --> 27:44.750
This repeated emotional tug-of-war

27:44.750 --> 27:46.680
easily makes people lose their senses.

27:46.680 --> 27:48.000
Gradually, they turn into

27:48.000 --> 27:49.930
nothing more than an obedient pet.

27:51.310 --> 27:53.720
But people are not pets.

27:53.960 --> 27:55.690
They will always try to escape.

27:56.400 --> 27:57.570
But what if the pain of leaving

27:57.570 --> 28:00.170
is so great that it makes
them lose their minds?

28:07.850 --> 28:09.780
Take my coat to wear on the way back.

28:09.880 --> 28:11.120
You're covered in blood.

28:11.120 --> 28:13.250
You'll scare people walking outside.

28:14.110 --> 28:14.790
Thank you.

28:17.510 --> 28:19.710
Has everything been sorted out at home?

28:20.310 --> 28:21.570
It's all taken care of.

28:21.680 --> 28:22.740
Thanks for asking.

28:23.160 --> 28:24.480
I've been on leave long enough.

28:24.480 --> 28:26.580
I still need to head back to the hospital.

28:26.580 --> 28:28.240
I have my car. Let me drive you.

28:28.400 --> 28:28.860
No need.

28:29.440 --> 28:31.380
You've been through a lot today
and must be exhausted.

28:31.380 --> 28:32.660
I'll just get a taxi.

28:33.160 --> 28:34.420
Besides, don't forget

28:34.510 --> 28:36.840
you still need to find a lawyer
for Yuan Ye.

28:40.250 --> 28:41.910
Alright, I'll head off first.

28:49.640 --> 28:50.480
Keep in touch.

28:52.030 --> 28:53.090
I still have so much

28:53.160 --> 28:54.290
to talk to you about.

28:55.550 --> 28:56.070
Sure.

29:09.480 --> 29:10.320
Yan Ling,

29:10.790 --> 29:12.310
we've already drafted

29:12.310 --> 29:13.820
Ms. Yu's divorce agreement

29:13.820 --> 29:15.800
and sent it to both her
and her husband today.

29:15.800 --> 29:17.080
If there are no issues,

29:17.270 --> 29:18.880
they can file for divorce

29:18.880 --> 29:20.940
at the Civil Affairs Bureau anytime.

29:21.110 --> 29:22.240
Wow, that was quick.

29:22.310 --> 29:23.310
Thank you so much.

29:23.620 --> 29:24.550
You're welcome.

29:25.590 --> 29:26.070
Well,

29:27.550 --> 29:28.570
Ms. Yu

29:28.960 --> 29:30.070
is actually quite capable

29:30.070 --> 29:31.400
of protecting herself.

29:32.680 --> 29:34.350
I hope she can move on soon.

29:35.240 --> 29:36.920
I really feel sorry for her.

29:37.330 --> 29:38.000
Otherwise,

29:38.270 --> 29:39.930
I wouldn't have bothered you.

29:41.810 --> 29:43.230
It's no trouble.

29:43.790 --> 29:44.440
Of course,

29:44.700 --> 29:46.790
we hope there won't
be more cases like this.

29:46.790 --> 29:47.400
Hey,

29:47.830 --> 29:49.760
I have another humble favor to ask.

29:51.440 --> 29:52.960
Could you refer me

29:52.960 --> 29:54.590
to a criminal defense lawyer?

29:54.590 --> 29:56.050
There's a young girl I know

29:56.200 --> 29:58.170
who's been detained on charges
of intentional assault.

29:58.170 --> 29:59.500
She's still very young,

29:59.890 --> 30:02.110
and I'm afraid this case
will ruin her whole life

30:02.110 --> 30:03.350
if it's mishandled.

30:03.940 --> 30:05.310
I really want to help her.

30:05.310 --> 30:06.200
A lawyer can only

30:06.200 --> 30:08.810
take the case with formal authorization
from the client or her family.

30:08.810 --> 30:09.920
I'll arrange a colleague to assess

30:09.920 --> 30:11.240
the situation tomorrow.

30:11.240 --> 30:11.770
Alright,

30:12.270 --> 30:13.150
thank you.

30:13.750 --> 30:14.780
Goodbye.

30:19.160 --> 30:19.960
What's wrong?

30:20.160 --> 30:20.830
What kind of people

30:20.830 --> 30:23.550
does Yan Ling hang around with all day?

30:24.480 --> 30:26.070
All those girls around her

30:26.070 --> 30:26.970
are so

30:27.350 --> 30:28.880
secretive and odd.

30:29.490 --> 30:30.240
I have no idea.

30:30.240 --> 30:31.240
It's hard to tell.

30:32.590 --> 30:34.450
She's just likes helping people.

30:35.060 --> 30:36.180
Isn't she just like you in that regard?

30:36.180 --> 30:37.510
Don't compare me to her.

30:38.710 --> 30:42.140
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

30:41.270 --> 30:42.750
I'll take care of

30:42.770 --> 30:44.570
any follow-up paperwork later.

30:44.820 --> 30:46.680
Just call me if anything comes up.

30:47.350 --> 30:56.350
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

30:47.400 --> 30:49.110
We've settled this peacefully.

30:49.110 --> 30:50.110
I hope you can move on

30:50.110 --> 30:51.240
and live a good life.

31:02.680 --> 31:04.210
Find someone nice someday,

31:04.440 --> 31:05.500
and treat her well.

31:05.730 --> 31:06.860
Stop drinking, too.

31:11.890 --> 31:14.420
I'll bring the baby to see you
after it's born,

31:14.620 --> 31:15.850
if you'd like.

31:17.620 --> 31:18.380
Xinxin.

31:20.160 --> 31:22.120
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

31:22.360 --> 31:23.080
Take care.

31:28.570 --> 31:30.350
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

31:32.000 --> 31:33.600
Thank you and Attorney Zhou.

31:33.800 --> 31:35.880
We've really put you through
a lot of trouble.

31:35.880 --> 31:36.750
You're welcome.

31:36.750 --> 31:37.680
Thank you again.

31:50.580 --> 31:53.330
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

31:53.430 --> 31:56.940
[International Departure]

32:11.880 --> 32:14.140
Your mom will be so happy
to have you back.

32:14.640 --> 32:15.750
Take good care of yourself,

32:15.750 --> 32:17.150
and focus on recovering.

32:18.800 --> 32:20.400
She'll definitely blame me.

32:21.350 --> 32:25.010
I didn't listen to her, and now
I've learned my lesson the hard way.

32:26.470 --> 32:27.620
All moms say things like that.

32:27.620 --> 32:29.050
They're just worried.

32:29.790 --> 32:30.800
Deep down,

32:30.880 --> 32:32.480
they always love their kids,

32:33.340 --> 32:36.540
especially now that she's going
to be a grandmother soon.

32:42.030 --> 32:42.680
Thank you.

32:44.240 --> 32:45.900
I wish you were my real sister.

32:46.590 --> 32:48.720
Send me photos once the baby's born.

32:53.070 --> 32:54.030
I'm leaving now.

32:54.640 --> 32:55.440
Safe travels.

33:08.730 --> 33:14.340
[Reception]

33:14.860 --> 33:15.690
[Reception]

33:25.590 --> 33:26.110
Here.

33:33.110 --> 33:33.910
What's wrong?

33:34.240 --> 33:35.240
You don't want it?

33:36.350 --> 33:37.930
Does your wound hurt?

33:37.980 --> 33:39.240
Should I go get the doctor?

33:39.240 --> 33:39.830
No need.

33:40.480 --> 33:41.680
Take a look yourself.

33:42.480 --> 33:44.280
Is this soup or just a bowl of oil?

33:44.790 --> 33:47.220
I'll go home and make it again.

33:47.720 --> 33:49.750
Or how about I make you
some pork ribs soup?

33:49.750 --> 33:51.160
I don't eat pork.

33:51.550 --> 33:52.950
Can't you ever remember?

33:53.880 --> 33:54.310
You...

33:55.720 --> 33:57.120
Did you ever tell me that?

33:57.270 --> 33:58.510
Can't I say it now?

34:00.400 --> 34:01.660
Alright, just go home.

34:02.440 --> 34:03.770
I want to sleep for a bit.

34:11.800 --> 34:12.400
It's fine.

34:13.320 --> 34:14.110
I was just nearby,

34:14.110 --> 34:15.440
so I came to check on you.

34:15.440 --> 34:16.170
Don't worry.

34:16.360 --> 34:18.159
I won't tell anyone you're here.

34:21.670 --> 34:23.590
You could just get a straw for hot drinks

34:23.590 --> 34:24.449
and stick it in.

34:24.880 --> 34:26.880
That way you won't end up
drinking all the oil.

34:26.880 --> 34:27.810
I'll go find one.

34:55.920 --> 34:56.590
It's nice.

35:00.110 --> 35:00.800
Jealous?

35:02.030 --> 35:03.320
I'm just good at being born lucky,

35:03.320 --> 35:05.120
that's why I get a room like this.

35:05.190 --> 35:06.960
I'm talking about your perks.

35:08.030 --> 35:10.230
Good looks plus a privileged background.

35:10.230 --> 35:11.670
Total charm magnet.

35:12.920 --> 35:14.050
In just a few months,

35:14.320 --> 35:15.550
you've got those girls

35:15.550 --> 35:16.880
head over heels for you.

35:17.510 --> 35:18.640
You're good at this.

35:19.280 --> 35:20.280
Loving this, huh?

35:22.190 --> 35:22.990
Can't help it.

35:24.150 --> 35:25.810
I'm just naturally likeable.

35:26.070 --> 35:27.470
You don't actually think

35:28.150 --> 35:30.880
you're some smooth player who's
got it all figured out, do you?

35:30.880 --> 35:31.590
Happy now?

35:36.230 --> 35:37.560
What are you getting at?

35:40.320 --> 35:41.860
All the girls you go after

35:42.000 --> 35:43.330
are just barely adults,

35:44.360 --> 35:45.560
naive,

35:46.190 --> 35:47.520
from regular families.

35:48.110 --> 35:50.360
They lack both material comfort
and real affection.

35:50.360 --> 35:52.610
Give them a little warmth,

35:53.320 --> 35:55.120
and they fall for you right away.

35:55.950 --> 35:56.970
If I were you,

35:58.000 --> 35:59.450
preying on girls like this

35:59.450 --> 36:01.920
and almost getting myself
killed in the process?

36:01.920 --> 36:02.960
I'd be

36:03.630 --> 36:04.510
embarrassed.

36:10.670 --> 36:11.360
Found it.

36:12.590 --> 36:13.390
That's right.

36:13.630 --> 36:14.440
Use the right method,

36:14.440 --> 36:16.970
then you won't burn your mouth
drinking soup.

36:17.800 --> 36:18.460
Changning,

36:19.670 --> 36:20.710
think carefully

36:20.710 --> 36:21.970
what I told you before.

36:23.000 --> 36:23.800
Get well soon.

36:30.670 --> 36:31.800
What did he tell you?

36:35.290 --> 36:35.980
Speak.

36:38.150 --> 36:38.880
Are you mute?

36:44.000 --> 36:45.480
He said you don't love me.

36:53.630 --> 36:54.760
Do you believe him?

36:58.480 --> 36:58.840
I...

37:02.840 --> 37:03.570
have no idea.

37:04.760 --> 37:06.090
No idea, huh?

37:06.880 --> 37:08.820
Yes, he's right.

37:09.280 --> 37:10.320
I don't love you.

37:10.880 --> 37:12.400
Why aren't you leaving, then?

37:12.400 --> 37:14.130
Stop putting on an act here!

37:14.240 --> 37:14.880
I'm sorry.

37:14.920 --> 37:15.840
I'm sorry, Feng.

37:15.840 --> 37:17.260
I know you love me.

37:17.400 --> 37:18.800
Those messages you sent me,

37:18.800 --> 37:19.590
the photos,

37:19.590 --> 37:20.190
and the songs,

37:20.190 --> 37:21.360
I've seen and heard them all.

37:21.360 --> 37:23.590
I was just... I was just afraid
you'd leave me.

37:23.590 --> 37:24.280
Shut up.

37:25.360 --> 37:27.710
You are really annoying.

37:32.240 --> 37:33.840
I got stabbed just to be with you.

37:33.840 --> 37:34.710
And you still have the nerve to cry?

37:34.710 --> 37:35.630
I'm sorry.

37:38.150 --> 37:39.110
I'm sorry, Feng.

37:39.110 --> 37:39.840
I'm sorry.

37:40.070 --> 37:40.930
Get out.

37:41.480 --> 37:43.840
I'm sorry. I'll come
see you again tomorrow.

37:43.840 --> 37:45.240
Get some good rest first.

37:52.400 --> 37:54.970
[Luo Liang, Lihai Renxin Hospital]

38:00.110 --> 38:01.310
[Doctor Profile: Luo Liang, Male,
Associate Chief Physician]

38:01.340 --> 38:02.460
[Deputy Director of Outpatient
Department, Doctor of Psychiatry]

38:02.480 --> 38:03.050
[Master's Supervisor in Psychology]

38:03.080 --> 38:03.810
[National Certified Level 2
Psychological Counselor]

38:05.480 --> 38:06.350
Luo Liang.

38:11.390 --> 38:15.050
[Dongchuan Provincial Detention Center]

38:22.050 --> 38:22.740
Quiet.

38:35.810 --> 38:38.170
Regarding why Yuan Ye hurt Xu Feng,

38:38.210 --> 38:40.100
this is all we know so far.

38:40.440 --> 38:42.390
Everything points against
Yuan Ye right now.

38:40.640 --> 38:44.220
[Xinsheng International Law Firm]

38:44.760 --> 38:47.020
Is Yuan Ye still holding up emotionally?

38:47.030 --> 38:48.960
She said everything was her fault.

38:49.300 --> 38:50.720
If I go locked up,

38:51.950 --> 38:54.120
will Feng forgive me?

38:56.440 --> 38:58.570
You need to think more about yourself.

38:58.650 --> 39:00.740
Your whole life's still ahead of you.

39:02.210 --> 39:03.840
Have you ever thought about it?

39:03.840 --> 39:05.420
If he doesn't make it,

39:06.360 --> 39:07.870
you'll be a murderer.

39:09.080 --> 39:10.650
If Feng dies,

39:12.980 --> 39:15.110
I don't have anything left to live for.

39:20.360 --> 39:22.210
I'm so sorry, Feng.

39:22.840 --> 39:23.880
Should we try shifting

39:23.880 --> 39:24.880
our defense

39:24.880 --> 39:27.190
to accidental injury?

39:28.110 --> 39:29.960
Putting her own statement aside,

39:29.960 --> 39:32.380
the simple fact that
she brought the weapon

39:32.670 --> 39:35.330
makes it really hard to claim it
was an accident.

39:38.550 --> 39:40.510
I know this sounds ridiculous,

39:41.670 --> 39:43.040
but listen.

39:44.220 --> 39:45.670
One of my female students

39:46.180 --> 39:48.980
has already suffered terribly
because of Xu Feng.

39:49.040 --> 39:50.560
I just can't stand by

39:50.630 --> 39:51.760
and watch Yuan Ye

39:51.760 --> 39:53.250
go down the same path.

39:53.670 --> 39:54.400
Mi,

39:54.860 --> 39:55.320
I know

39:55.320 --> 39:57.320
I've caused you a lot of trouble

39:57.540 --> 39:59.000
and put you in a tough spot.

39:59.400 --> 40:01.840
But please, can you try
to think of another way?

40:01.840 --> 40:02.590
Don't let her ruin

40:02.590 --> 40:03.320
her whole life

40:03.320 --> 40:05.350
at such a young age

40:05.800 --> 40:07.230
over a guy who never even cherished her.

40:07.230 --> 40:08.880
she's so young.

40:18.480 --> 40:20.760
We've talked about this before.

40:21.450 --> 40:23.180
The best approach right now

40:23.200 --> 40:26.540
is to get the victim's forgiveness

40:26.710 --> 40:29.370
and offer reasonable
financial compensation.

40:29.400 --> 40:31.710
That's the only thing that might help

40:31.840 --> 40:33.170
with the final verdict.

40:34.230 --> 40:36.400
But looking at Yuan Ye's family situation,

40:36.400 --> 40:40.060
there's no way they can come up
with that much compensation money.

40:40.110 --> 40:42.480
Have you had any contact
with the victim's side?

40:42.480 --> 40:43.800
Xu Feng's family runs

40:43.800 --> 40:44.760
big businesses overseas.

40:44.760 --> 40:46.800
Small amounts of money
won't mean anything to them.

40:46.800 --> 40:47.760
His father had

40:47.760 --> 40:49.290
huge expectations for him.

40:49.300 --> 40:51.900
Now his son's been stabbed
for no clear reason.

40:51.990 --> 40:54.390
This is going to be
an extremely tough case.

41:00.710 --> 41:02.760
Can I be there when you talk to Xu Feng

41:03.090 --> 41:04.220
about a settlement?

41:12.050 --> 41:16.230
[The Dark Romance]

41:32.400 --> 41:32.960
Miss.

41:33.240 --> 41:34.860
Would you like some drinks, sir?

41:34.860 --> 41:35.560
No.

41:36.230 --> 41:37.900
I'd like to ask you about someone.

41:37.900 --> 41:39.370
She used to work here.
